      • getUsersByUserAttributeStream

        default Stream<String> getUsersByUserAttributeStream​(RealmModel realm,
                                                     String name,
                                                     String value)
        Searches for federated users that have an attribute with the specified name and value.
        Parameters:
        realm - a reference to the realm.
        name - the attribute name.
        value - the attribute value.
        Returns:
        a non-null Stream of users that match the search criteria.
